                     <interp inst="t18470705-1694-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp> for unlawfully obtaining 1 half-crown, 7 shillings, 1 groat, and 2 pence, the monies of <persName id="t18470705-name-757" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-757" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-757" type="surname" value="WATTS"></interp>
