                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-760" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN DONALLY.</persName>
                  </hi> I am gunner in the Royal Artillery—the prisoner was in that corps. On Saturday, the 19th of June, he showed me such a thing as this token, and told me he would try and pass it.</p>
